Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咪  我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.89,0:01:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大石先生  好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且早就超過約好的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡警先生從中午開始就一直守在門外了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人來換班也很可憐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.22,0:02:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我覺得如果是大石先生的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會有什麼問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.79,0:02:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「黃鶯」呼叫本部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩具被射殺的屍體處理完畢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總部收到  加快作業
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到情報  換班的警察即將趕到目標家中了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃不變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉刑警也沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚  古手神社裡的所有人都會突然消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為「鬼隱」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大石先生發生了什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.45,0:02:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只聽說他們有和警局聯絡過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:55.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你們也回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.31,0:02:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後還有我們在  放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:01.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不回家  你們家人會擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都說明天會再來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼明天就要好好準備一些點心才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是他們留下來吃晚餐的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吃速食  來做一些菜好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是真的會來臨還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:35.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一直這麼不安地度過這一夜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨花？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就不要換睡衣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接穿這樣睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果發生了什麼事  也能馬上應變  沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙都子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防萬一啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:56.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  神社周圍設置的陷阱數  是平常的三倍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:04:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  不確定的未來對現在的我來說  反而是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？你肚子餓了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間馬上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以  不可以被這樣的感情給淹沒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要相信  要相信  要相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊  羽入
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會反抗的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算明天一樣會被殺也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要反抗這今晚就會被殺的命運！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是「鳳4」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包含目標在內  有兩人逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們追
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳踩到陷阱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「鳳6」「鳳7」  目標逃往後山了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點抓住他們！
Comment: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:17.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（"他"沒錯）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「鳳6」明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是什麼聲音？槍聲嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:28.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是摔炮  可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沙都子吧  真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意監視周圍情況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她們逃進民宅就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「鳳9」發現目標
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在後山的北面  請求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們兩個方向感很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.19,0:05:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點抓住她們  真的會跟丟的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.59,0:05:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他  他們是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梨花你所說的「東京」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了  快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.51,0:05:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抓住的話  可是會被殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魅她們家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下的秘密房間的話很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能和外界聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨花！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙都子  快跑！連你也會被殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  梨花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  沙都子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:26.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種衣服  果然幕後黑手是鷹野嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要知道了犯人是鷹野的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在這裡被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下個世界裡也一定會有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能死  如果沒把這個記憶繼承下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑  梨花！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙都子！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡交給我  你快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我在這裡逃跑的話  沙都子她就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這絕對不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要拼上這條命  我也不會讓沙都子被殺的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我不活下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才掌握到的事實  就會消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒把記憶保留下來  那就白白浪費掉這條命了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要拋棄沙都子  也要活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我辦不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是個笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都知道你們的真面目了  還不選擇逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我不會逃避的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運是可以打破的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經有人教了我這個道理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭一！蕾娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.86,0:07:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魅音  詩音！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼會來這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜她說有不好的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像被什麼人盯著的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有感覺到氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:51.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧你能察覺到  不愧是蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們回去拿了能當作武器的東西 就趕回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:08:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真想不到會在這裡被大家所救
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來的時候巡警都倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們打算要躲到魅音家去  地下那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭具殿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也贊成  那裡面有好幾條秘密通道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就要快  追兵馬上就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:25.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點回話！「鳳6」「鳳9」怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.18,0:08:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才幾個小鬼就搞成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不是普通的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中可是有被稱為「御社神轉世」的孩子在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  真正的御社神  現在才正要誕生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到了  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿圭  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  走這條路的話會被追上的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打趴他們  開出一條血路來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  順利的話  連車子都能搶到手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開車的工作就交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魅  你有駕照嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是非常時期  小事就別在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呵呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真是個好主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就決定了  我們上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡！抓住她！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.49,0:09:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解決一個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要小心背後啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給圭一君了  拜託囉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:09:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒殺了他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心  是用刀背砍的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種小鬼的把戲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因為是小孩就小看了我們  那才教人困擾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是社團活動的成果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是收拾乾淨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕鬆獲勝了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為大家齊心協力一起戰鬥嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手有6個  我們也是6個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想少了任何一個人都辦不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  大家齊心協力的話  一定能打破命運的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手也不愧是專業人士  一開始那些傢伙就已經察覺了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:10:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算什麼  我們更有士氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起的話  就沒什麼好怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽入  你還是一樣  早就放棄了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就好好看個清楚  這股垂死掙扎的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運正在…改變！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭一…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷹野！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿圭  振作點！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.63,0:11:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要退場了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們快跑…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…騙人！騙人…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿圭你怎麼會這樣就死掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.76,0:12:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…快跑啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只能考慮要怎麼活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在這裡不是圭一君想要的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  快跑啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…要活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方人越來越多了  趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小魅？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我留下來當誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我拖延時間的時候  大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:12:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有爭論的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有保護沙都子的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜  梨花就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走  梨花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魅…魅！魅!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微休息一下  知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知…道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐這笨蛋…耍什麼帥啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:32.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小魅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.48,0:13:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？你沒事嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魅音…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思哦  她已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小詩  她們兩個就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.57,0:13:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連續離奇死亡事件  全都是鷹野小姐幹的好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:14:01.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做御社神大人的代行者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是代行者  而是我所賜的天罰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來村中所發生的作祟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我所賜的天罰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那時  我將超越人類
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:19.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為御社神本身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管鷹野小姐做什麼  都只是扮家家酒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是無法成為御社神大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會成為的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我就將成為…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要知道御社神大人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去我受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了我…快點殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:14:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙都子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩音…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有一分一秒也要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.54,0:15:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:11.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連悟史君的份一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  從誰開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要殺沙都子！求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要殺我就儘管來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但求求你放過沙都子！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵呵  我會考慮一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:53.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得她有來求我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說該怎麼辦呢  沙都子妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那來猜個謎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青花菜和花椰菜  哪個是綠色的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花…青花菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要殺我對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  當然要殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王感染者的屍體是作戰的關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你將成為遙遠的「東京」那裡的醜惡政治的鬥爭工具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時  也將為鬼之淵傳說畫下句點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確像是鷹野會做的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安  梨花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  求饒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:17:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  要殺我的話  不要等我睡著才下手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想死得舒服一點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會很痛哦  活生生地切開你的肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子被你切開的事  我要深深烙印在靈魂上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了在下次相遇的時候  要能回想起你就是敵人來！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.74,0:17:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又…又失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  羽入
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.88,0:17:41.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們竭盡全力了  只差一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.51,0:17:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我是不會灰心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這個記憶沒有繼承下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算下個雛見澤只有幾天就會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要不擇手段地活著活著活下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:18:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  下次一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的死  我絕不會忘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不會忘的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算梨花忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.19,0:18:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一定會告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和大家一起活在一個快樂的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一點就能打破命運了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家齊心協力努力過了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.93,0:18:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果反抗命運的意志  再更堅強一點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.31,0:19:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們大家都相信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只差了一點點就能達到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  梨花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很感謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這次也只能放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.26,0:19:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算大家齊心協力  也沒有發生奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡沒有發生的理由  蕾娜是明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的相信了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚  啊嗚啊嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是個無能為力的弱小存在而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能袖手旁觀的我  就算相信了也沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.45,0:19:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡會發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我們再加上你的話  我想奇跡一定會發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:10.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要跟命運戰鬥的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.32,0:20:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是我們的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往下一個世界去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩千人！是兩千人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先應該制裁  想出這個爛點子的「東京」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛見澤症候群  就如我所說的  是一種非常危險的疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果外洩的話  受害者就不只有兩千人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.74,0:20:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須實施必要的處理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:21:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把損害控制在最小吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.87,0:21:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始消毒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.82,0:21:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一小隊報告本部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,營林所消毒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射殺脫逃者4名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.16,0:21:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二小隊報告本部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約有十名脫逃者逃往山上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.47,0:21:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在掃蕩中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.79,0:21:52.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無罰無神  因罰生懼  有懼乃敬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻即是神明降臨之際
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我亦為御社大神！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.93,0:23:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我就想問了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.63,0:23:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.91,0:23:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽入你說的「啊嗚啊嗚」是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.26,0:23:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個是意識的單純表現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.64,0:23:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有疑問的時候會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.96,0:23:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.85,0:24:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把「在情況不妙的時候  讓周遭知道我真的很難過」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.19,0:24:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「希望不要再讓我這麼難過了的說」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.61,0:24:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的感情 用可愛的形式來表現出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.54,0:24:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…啊嗚啊嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.96,0:24:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是被我說中了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.48,0:24:14.11,yokoku,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.25,0:24:16.20,yokoku,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭{\1c&H0000ff&}囃{\r}篇  其一
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.56,0:24:17.14,yokoku,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三四
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.44,0:24:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚  啊嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.30,0:24:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對的說  不對的說
